22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebest%20cordless%20vacuums%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Its%20overall%20cleaning%20performance%20was%20impressive%20%E2%80%94%20as%20was%20its%20appearance%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20critiques%20you%20should%20know%20about%20before%20you%20splurge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20holds%20the%20samsung%20vacuum%20on%20carpet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675202288fb3f94e5073aba9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fefd06b1-a270-4ad1-b7ce-047caf401a64%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESetup%20and%20Design%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22parts%20of%20the%20samsung%20vacuums%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675202284adc4cc13434d4e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samsung%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20Cordless%20Stick%20Vacuum%20is%20designed%20with%20aesthetics%20in%20mind.%20It%20has%20a%20sleek%20round%20base%20with%20a%20fluted%20exterior%20and%20satin%20finish%2C%20and%20it%20could%20pass%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20contemporary%20decor.%20The%20vacuum%20has%20a%20matching%20finish%2C%20creating%20a%20seamless%20appearance%20when%20it's%20docked.%20It's%20definitely%20one%20of%20the%20most%20stylish%20vacuums%20I've%20seen%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20mind%20having%20it%20out%20in%20the%20open%20in%20one%20of%20my%20main%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20off%20to%20the%20best%20start%20with%20this%20vacuum.%20Despite%20having%20assembled%20dozens%20of%20cordless%20vacuums%20in%20my%20career%2C%20I%20had%20a%20surprisingly%20hard%20time%20setting%20it%20up.%20After%20unboxing%20all%20the%20pieces%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20put%20the%20vacuum%20itself%20together%20with%20no%20problem%2C%20but%20the%20design%20of%20the%20base%20wasn't%20intuitive.%20The%20side%20that%20I%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20back%20of%20the%20base%20was%20actually%20the%20front%2C%20which%20means%20you%20have%20to%20place%20the%20vacuum%20onto%20the%20back%20of%20the%20dock.%20It's%20a%20strange%20design%20choice%20that%20prioritizes%20aesthetics%20over%20function%2C%20and%20if%20you%20place%20the%20base%20too%20close%20to%20the%20wall%2C%20you'll%20end%20up%20banging%20the%20vacuum%20against%20it%20every%20time%20you%20put%20it%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20thing%20that%20had%20me%20scratching%20my%20head%20was%20that%20there%20are%20three%20accessories%20%E2%80%94%20a%20powered%20pet%20tool%2C%20combination%20tool%2C%20and%20crevice%20tool%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20there's%20nowhere%20to%20store%20them.%20I%20spent%20longer%20than%20I%20care%20to%20admit%20prying%20at%20different%20panels%20on%20the%20base%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20compartment%20where%20I%20could%20put%20the%20accessories.%20(I%20also%20read%20through%20the%20manual%2C%20which%20offered%20no%20insights.)%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20there's%20just%20not%20any%20storage%20for%20these%20pieces%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20negative%20if%20you%20ask%20me.%20What's%20the%20point%20of%20having%20a%20big%2C%20stylish%20base%20that's%20meant%20to%20be%20displayed%20in%20your%20home%20if%20you%20then%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20attachments%20separately%20in%20a%20closet%20somewhere%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4a973ff-3843-460c-8a0c-d3fb144071cd%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20Stick%20vacuum%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20see%20how%20the%20Samsung%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20stacks%20up%20against%20other%20cordless%20vacuums%2C%20I%20tested%20it%20in%20my%20home%20for%20around%20a%20month.%20I%20predominantly%20used%20it%20to%20vacuum%20the%20main%20floor%20of%20my%20home%2C%20which%20is%20around%201%2C000%20square%20feet%20and%20features%20hardwood%20and%20linoleum%20floors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20area%20rugs.%20Because%20I%20share%20my%20home%20with%20two%20long-hair%20dogs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20short-haired%20cat%2C%20there's%20no%20shortage%20of%20dirt%2C%20dust%2C%20and%20pet%20hair%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20put%20the%20vacuum%20through%20its%20paces%20to%20find%20out%20where%20it%20excelled%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20it%20fell%20short.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f37628d-1c51-478f-88a6-0f198b273893%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEase%20of%20Use%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20uses%20a%20handheld%20vacuum%20on%20a%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675202288fb3f94e5073aba5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20easily%20converts%20to%20a%20handheld%2C%20where%20I'll%20use%20the%20powered%20pet%20tool%20to%20clean%20upholstery.%20%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20cordless%20vacuum%20is%20fairly%20lightweight%20at%20just%20over%20six%20pounds%2C%20and%20I%20found%20that%20it%20was%20very%20easy%20to%20carry%20around.%20It%20has%20an%20on%2Foff%20switch%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20vacuum%2C%20as%20well%20as%20buttons%20to%20increase%20or%20decrease%20suction%20and%20a%20fancy%20digital%20display%20screen.%20When%20I%20turned%20the%20vacuum%20on%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20even%20asked%20me%20to%20select%20my%20preferred%20language.%20I%20also%20love%20that%20it%20has%20a%20telescoping%20wand%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20adjust%20its%20height.%20This%20makes%20it%20much%20more%20ergonomic%20to%20use%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20a%20taller%20individual.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you're%20done%20cleaning%2C%20you%20simply%20dock%20this%20vacuum%20back%20on%20its%20base%2C%20which%20then%20automatically%20empties%20the%20dust%20bin.%20The%20dock%20also%20makes%20sure%20the%20vacuum%20is%20fully%20charged%20and%20ready%20to%20go%20the%20next%20time%20you%20need%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241d8d610-c39e-43a8-9143-1fc583f741ff%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECleaning%20Performance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20vacuum%20cleanerhead%20with%20led%20lights%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675202288fb3f94e5073aba6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20has%205%20cleaning%20settings%2C%20including%20an%20AI%20mode%20that%20adjusts%20suction%20based%20on%20floor%20type.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20aspects%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20is%20that%20it%20has%20five%20different%20cleaning%20settings%20%E2%80%94%20Min%2C%20AI%2C%20Mid%2C%20Max%2C%20and%20Jet%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20maximum%20suction%20power%20of%20280%20air%20watts.%20Most%20cordless%20vacuums%20only%20have%20three%20settings%2C%20and%20I've%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Beco%26quot%3B%20modes%20are%20often%20too%20weak%20to%20be%20useful%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bmax%26quot%3B%20modes%20drain%20the%20battery%20way%20too%20quickly.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20I%20appreciate%20having%20more%20suction%20levels%20in%20between%20to%20find%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20performance%20and%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20you%20turn%20this%20vacuum%20on%2C%20it%20defaults%20to%20AI%20mode%2C%20which%20automatically%20adjusts%20its%20suction%20based%20on%20the%20floor%20type%20to%20maximize%20battery%20life%20%E2%80%94%20it%20functions%20similarly%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BAuto%26quot%3B%20mode%20you'll%20find%20on%20cordless%20vacuums%20from%20Shark%2C%20Dyson%2C%20and%20Tineco.%20This%20setting%20worked%20surprisingly%20well%2C%20increasing%20suction%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20moved%20onto%20carpeting%20and%20dropping%20it%20back%20down%20when%20it%20sensed%20hard%20floors%2C%20It%20also%20boosted%20suction%20when%20I%20drove%20it%20through%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20dirt%20or%20debris.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20used%20the%20Bespoke%20Jet%20AI%20vacuum%20for%20everyday%20cleaning%20around%20my%20house%2C%20and%20I%20also%20put%20it%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%2C%20using%20it%20to%20suck%20up%20debris%20like%20uncooked%20rice%2C%20coffee%20grounds%2C%20and%20baby%20powder%20off%20different%20types%20of%20flooring.%20Because%20it%20offers%20more%20settings%20than%20your%20average%20vacuum%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20dial%20in%20the%20suction%20to%20the%20task%20at%20hand%2C%20and%20it%20did%20a%20(mostly)%20great%20job%20on%20both%20hard%20floors%20and%20carpeting%20thanks%20to%20its%20dual%20brushrolls.%20However%2C%20it%20struggled%20with%20larger%20debris%20like%20cereal%20and%20rice%20on%20hardwoods%20%E2%80%94%20the%20floorhead%20is%20too%20low%20and%20struggled%20to%20suck%20up%20the%20large%20pieces%2C%20often%20just%20pushing%20them%20around%20the%20floor%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20area%20where%20this%20vacuum%20struggled%20was%20cleaning%20up%20pet%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20long%20pet%20hair%2C%20in%20particular.%20After%20cleaning%20the%20main%20floor%20of%20my%20home%2C%20where%20my%20two%20golden%20retrievers%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20there%20was%20%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20hair%20wrapped%20around%20the%20vacuum's%20brushroll%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20use%20scissors%20to%20cut%20it%20off.%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20such%20an%20expensive%20vacuum%20doesn't%20have%20any%