%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Finn%20poses%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20gallery's%20exhibits%2C%20she%20looks%20right%20at%20home.%20After%20all%2C%20she's%20worked%20in%20the%20art%20world%20for%20over%2020%20years%2C%20climbing%20the%20ranks%20and%20building%20rapport%20at%20galleries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Bortolami.%20The%20latest%20feather%20in%20her%20cap%20is%20helming%20this%20year's%20Art%20Basel%20Miami%20Beach%20show%20as%20its%20new%20director.%20Her%20directorship%20started%20in%20September%202023%2C%20and%20she's%20spent%20the%20past%20year%20planning%20the%202024%20art%20fair%2C%20set%20to%20commence%20publicly%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bridget%20Finn%20stands%20with%20Caitlin%20Keogh's%20Procession%2C%202024.%20%C2%A9%20Caitlin%20Keogh%20(courtesy%20of%20the%20artist%20and%20Bortolami%2C%20NY.)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674ddb2e9e9761932b4a29d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFinn%20posed%20in%20Bortolami's%20space%20showcasing%20Caitlin%20Keogh's%20Procession%2C%202024.%20%C2%A9%20Caitlin%20Keogh%20(Courtesy%20of%20the%20artist%20and%20Bortolami%2C%20NY.)%3Cp%3EPaola%20Chapdelaine%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThinking%20about%20the%20show%20as%20a%20platform%20and%20how%20to%20develop%20structures%20of%20support%20for%20peers%20was%20incredibly%20important%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Finn%20told%20me%20on%20a%20video%20call%20a%20week%20before%20we%20met%20at%20Bortolami%2C%20one%20of%20286%20galleries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbortolamigallery%2Fp%2FDChTPlaRdUV%2F%3Fimg_index%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresenting%20works%20at%20Art%20Basel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20been%20drawn%20to%20art%20as%20a%20way%20of%20forging%20cross-culture%20dialogue%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20art%20fairs%20are%20a%20huge%20player%20in%20this%20realm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShepherding%20an%20event%20as%20massive%20and%20multicultural%20as%20Art%20Basel%20is%20a%20tall%20order.%20Finn%20said%20she%20tackled%20it%20by%20taking%20%26quot%3Bthe%20role%20of%20a%20listener%26quot%3B%20and%20meeting%20with%20several%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20artists%2C%20%26quot%3Bconnoisseur%20collectors%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20gallerists%20that%20are%20interested%20in%20showcasing%20their%20exhibitions.%20The%20objective%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20to%20accommodate%20everyone's%20desired%20experience%20and%20%26quot%3Bhave%20the%20best%20show%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20Finn%20added%2C%20trying%20to%20meet%20everyone's%20needs%20was%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20when%20her%20team%20members%20mapped%20out%20the%20floor%20plan%20at%20the%20Miami%20Beach%20Convention%20Center%2C%20a%201.4%20million-square-foot%20venue%2C%20they%20had%20to%20consider%20multiple%20factors%3A%20how%20to%20physically%20plot%20booths%20and%20exhibitions%2C%20how%20to%20make%20the%20space%20easy%20to%20navigate%20for%20attendees%2C%20and%20how%20to%20sensibly%20connect%20different%20sectors%20in%20the%20massive%20building.%20If%20they%20made%20a%20change%20that%20affected%20a%20gallery's%20placement%20on%20the%20show%20floor%2C%20they%20had%20to%20ensure%20the%20gallery%20was%20aware%20and%20aligned%20with%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20everything%20in%20the%20art%20world%2C%20there%20was%20a%20balance%20of%20flexibility%20%E2%80%94%20figuring%20out%20where%20we%20can%20be%20flexible%20and%20then%20what%20is%20an%20absolute%20must%2C%26quot%3B%20Finn%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20learning%20curve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%2034%20galleries%20will%20make%20their%20Art%20Basel%20Miami%20Beach%20debut%2C%20the%20most%20first-time%20participants%20at%20the%20fair%20in%20over%2015%20years.%20They're%20%26quot%3Binternational%