t%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659fd26143bb77284b9c2815%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20DeCicca%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBitcoin's%20rally%20is%20driven%20by%20the%202024%20halving%20and%20a%20crypto-friendly%20US%20president-elect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAdrian%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20says%20bitcoin's%20price%20could%20rally%20to%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%2C%20however%2C%20should%20brace%20for%20a%20few%20pullbacks%20early%20next%20year%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perfect%20storm%20has%20converged%2C%20leading%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcrypto-stocks-bitcoin-record-miner-coinbase-microstrategy-robinhood-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rally%20for%20bitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20broader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-cryptocurrency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrypto%3C%2Fa%3E%20market.%20And%20while%20no%20one%20can%20be%20sure%20how%20this%20rally%20will%20play%20out%2C%20many%20look%20to%20bitcoin's%20historical%20behavior%20to%20predict%20its%20coming%20price%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBitcoin's%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20rally%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise%20to%20its%20enthusiasts%2C%20who%20anticipate%20a%20rally%20every%20four%20years%20kicked%20off%20by%20the%20halving%2C%20which%20cuts%20the%20rate%20of%20new%20coins%20created%20in%20half%2C%20lowering%20the%20supply.%20As%20demand%20outpaces%20tighter%20supply%2C%20it%20drives%20the%20price%20up%2C%20building%20momentum%20and%20attracting%20even%20more%20buyers.%20In%20this%20round%2C%20the%20halving%20took%20place%20on%20April%2019%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcmtassociation.org%2Fpresenter%2Fadrian-zdunczyk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdrian%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20chartered%20market%20technician%20who%20has%20been%20following%20bitcoin's%20price%20patterns%20since%202022%2C%20marks%20the%20reversal%20of%20this%20round's%20bear%20market%20beginning%20in%20January%202023%2C%20when%20it%20broke%20above%20a%20key%20resistance%20line%20of%20%2420%2C000%20and%20began%20gradually%20climbing%20until%20the%20halving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20new%20about%20this%20round%20is%20the%20US%20election%2C%20which%20rung%20in%20a%20crypto-friendly%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20helped%20kick%20bitcoin's%20rally%20into%20higher%20gear.%20Since%20November%205%2C%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin%20has%20surged%20by%2045%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20political%20environment%20turned%20more%20investor%20attention%20to%20the%20asset%2C%20noted%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%2C%20who%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20crypto%20consulting%20firm%20The%20Birb%20Nest.%20Trump%20has%20voiced%20support%20for%20crypto%20in%20several%20ways%2C%20including%20vowing%20to%20retain%20the%20bitcoin%20held%20by%20the%20US%20government%2C%20choosing%20a%20crypto-friendly%20replacement%20for%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20Chair%20Gary%20Gensler%2C%20who%20has%20brought%20numerous%20lawsuits%20against%20crypto%20firms%2C%20and%20removing%20taxes%20on%20bitcoin%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20political%20environment%2C%20the%20asset%20was%20set%20for%20a%20bull%20run%2C%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20bitcoin%20bull%20market%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20who%20is%20in%20the%20presidential%20seat%20too%20much%2C%20as%20in%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20a%20similar%20reaction%20to%20what%20it%20was%20with%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20with%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20it%20would've%20just%20taken%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e920fae7-0655-49d6-a18c-282d1676452f%5C%22%3EForecast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20digital%20asset%20hovers%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20above%20%24100%2C000%2C%20is%20it%20too%20late%20to%20buy%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20that%20question%20is%20personal%20and%20varies%20based%20on%20numerous%20factors%2C%20including%20an%20investor's%20risk%20tolerance%20and%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20is%20a%20breakout%20trader%2C%20he%20buys%20at%20the%20start%20of%20a%20breakout%20to%20the%20upside%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20high%2C%20sell%20higher%26quot%3B%20strategy.%20But%20for%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20bargain%20price%2C%20if%20bitcoin%20follows%20its%20historical%20behavior%2C%20there%20will%20be%20too%20much%20volatility%20moving%20ahead.%20Any%20correction%20would%20be%20a%20flash%20in%20the%20pan%20and%20hard%20to%20time%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20expects%20bitcoin's%20price%20to%20continue%20rallying%20into%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20Ahead%20of%20Trump's%20inauguration%20on%20January%2020%2C%20he's%20bracing%20for%20heightened%20anticipation%20as%20traders%20make%20bets%20on%20the%20event%2C%20a%20move%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20the%20rumor%2C%20sell%20the%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20follows%20the%20belief%20that%20many%20may%20take%20profits%20at%20high%20points%20ahead%20of%20anticipated%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20believes%20a%20correction%20would%20then%20follow%2C%20taking%20effect%20by%20late%20January%20and%20into%20February%2C%20resulting%20in%20at%20least%20two%20corrections%20at%2015%25%2C%20with%20the%20most%20likely%20scenario%20being%20three%20corrections%20at%2030%25%20before%20it%20moves%20into%20the%20final%20phase%20of%20its%20bull%20run%2C%20where%20it%20could%20hit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-outlook-crypto-rally-100000-standard-chartered-etf-microstrategy-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24200%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20this%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20expectation%20of%20a%20higher%20price%20is%20backed%20by%20an%20assumption%20that%20retail%20traders%20haven't%20fully%20joined%20the%20rally.%20He%20pointed%20to%20last%20week's%20Google%20search%20trends%2C%20which%20were%20only%20at%2044%25%20of%202021's%20search%20peak%20when%20the%20last%20bull%20rally%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20means%20that%20not%20even%20five%20out%20of%2010%20people%20versus%20the%20last%20peak%20in%202021%20are%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Zdu%C5%84czyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20market%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20because%20of%20the%20ETFs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EETFs%20don't%20only%20have%20institutional%20value%2C%20they%20have%20adoption%20value%20for%20retail%20investors%20who%20have%20been%20reluctant%20to%20buy%20the%20asset%20due%20to%20custody%20barriers%2C%20he%20said.%20As%20more%20participants%20are%20afforded%20the%20ability%20to%20access%20bitcoin%2C%20it%20could%20create%20a%20deeper%20and%20wider%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-target-and-corrections-for-this-bull-run-cmt-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733428456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc27e3895d82203032e1f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-target-and-corrections-for-this-bull-run-cmt-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20is%20following%20its%20historical%20four-year%20cycle.%20Here's%20what%20could%20happen%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A66%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.