Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladeshs-yunus-seeks-help-of-religious-leaders-in-collecting-accurate-info-about-attacks-on-minorities%2Famp_articleshow%2F116017113.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladeshs-yunus-seeks-help-of-religious-leaders-in-collecting-accurate-info-about-attacks-on-minorities%2Famp_articleshow%2F116017113.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Puts%20PROBA-3%20In%20Orbit.%20A%2010-Point%20Guide%20About%20The%20European%20Satellite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPROBA%2C%20short%20for%20Project%20for%20Onboard%20Anatomy%2C%20is%20a%20space%20programme%20under%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20or%20ESA.%20Under%20PROBA%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20series%20of%20satellite%20launches.%20Today's%20was%20the%20third%20in%20that%20series%2C%20hence%20the%20name%20PROBA-3.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPROBA-3%20is%20a%20solar%20mission.%20It's%20aim%20is%20to%20study%20the%20Sun's%20corona%20at%20a%20level%20of%20precision%20never%20done%20before.%20PROBA-3%20consists%20of%20two%20independent%2C%20three-axis%20stabilised%20spacecraft%20-%20the%20Coronagraph%20Spacecraft%20or%20CSC%2C%20which%20is%20310%20kg%20and%20the%20Occulter%20Spacecraft%20or%20OSC%2C%20which%20is%20240%20kg.%20Both%20spacecraft%20will%20have%20a%20highly%20elliptical%20orbit%20around%20Earth%20whose%20apogee%20or%20distance%20farthest%20from%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20planet%20at%20the%20equator%20will%20be%2060%2C500%20km.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%2C%20the%20mission%20will%20demonstrate%20'formation%20flying'%20within%20the%20context%20of%20a%20large-scale%20scientific%20experiment.%20The%20two%20spacecraft%20in%20orbit%20will%20create%20an%20approximately%20150-metre-long%20solar%20coronagraph%20to%20study%20the%20Sun's%20faint%20corona%20closer%20to%20the%20solar%20rim%20than%20has%20ever%20been%20achieved%20before.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBy%20flying%20in%20such%20a%20close%20formation%20-%20150%20metres%20-%20the%20Occulter%20Spacecraft%20will%20cast%20a%20precise%20shadow%20onto%20the%20Coronagraph's%20telescope%2C%20thereby%20blocking%20any%20direct%20sunlight.%20The%20Coronagraph%20will%20then%20be%20able%20to%20map%20and%20image%20the%20Sun's%20corona%20in%20the%20full%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20-%20which%20includes%20visible%20light%2C%20Ultraviolet%20radiation%20(UV%20rays)%20and%20Infra-Red%20radiation%20(IR).%20It%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20image%20the%20solar%20corona%20in%20polarised%20light%20-%20which%20is%20made%20up%20of%20waves%20that%20vibrate%20in%20a%20single%20plane%20and%20include%20linearly%2C%20circularly%2C%20and%20elliptically%20polarised%20lights.%20The%20CSC%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20this%20for%20many%20hours%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20scientific%20objective%20of%20the%20PROBA-3%20mission%20is%20to%20observe%20the%20Sun's%20corona%20at%201.1%20solar%20radius%20in%20the%20visible%20wavelength%20range%20(visible%20light).%20Solar%20radius%20is%20a%20unit%20of%20distance%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20size%20of%20stars%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Sun.%201%20solar%20radius%20equals%206.95700%20x%2010(to%20the%20power%208)%20meters%20or%20695%2C700%20km.%20This%20is%20roughly%20109%20times%20the%20radius%20of%20the%20Earth.%20This%20would%20make%20PROBA-3%20the%20most%20precise%20satellite%20to%20map%20and%20image%20the%20Sun's%20corona.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPROBA-3%20marks%20the%20next%20step%20in%20formation%20flying.%20As%20a%20world%20first%2C%20its%20two%20satellites%20-%20the%20Coronagraph%20spacecraft%20and%20the%20Occulter%20spacecraft%20-%20will%20maintain%20formation%20to%20a%20few%20millimetres%20and%20arc%20second%20precision%20at%20distances%20of%20around%20150%20metres%20of%20each%20other%20for%20six%20hours%20at%20a%20time%20per%2019-hour%2C%2036-minute%20orbit.%20In%20effect%20the%20pair%20will%20be%20forming%20a%20virtual%20giant%20satellite.%20And%20this%20will%20be%20achieved%20autonomously%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20guidance%20from%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENow%20that%20the%20two%20satellites%20have%20been%20successfully%20placed%20in%20orbit%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20short%20preparatory%20period%20for%20the%20two%20satellites%20in%20which%20some%20safety%20tests%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency.%20Because%20these%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20independent%20yet%20flying%20in%20tandem%20in%20close%20proximity%2C%20a%20collision%20manoeuvre%20test%20will%20be%20conducted.%20Once%20these%20tests%20are%20complete%2C%20the%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20placed%20into%20into%20a%20safe%20relative%20tandem%20orbit.%20They%20can%20then%20be%20left%20safely%20in%20with%20no%20risk%20of%20collision%20or%20running%20away%20from%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20PROBA-3%20satellites%20will%20repetitively%20demonstrate%20acquisition%2C%20rendezvous%2C%20proximity%20operations%2C%20formation%20flying%2C%20coronagraph%20observations%2C%20separation%20and%20convoy%20flying%20in%20every%20orbit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Europan%20Space%20Agency%2C%20the%20PROBA-3%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3BLaboratory%20in%20space%26quot%3B%20to%20validate%20strategies%2C%20guidance%2C%20navigation%20and%20control%2C%20and%20other%20algorithms%2C%20such%20as%20relative%20GPS%20navigation%2C%20previously%20tried%20in%20ground%20simulators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ESA%20said%20that%20this%20mission%20includes%20a%20rendezvous%20experiment.%20It%20will%20test%20sensors%20and%20algorithms%20for%20satellites%20to%20Rendezvous%20(cooperative%20and%20uncooperative)%20in%20elliptical%20orbit.%20This%20cutting-edge%20technology%20could%20be%20used%20for%20a%20future%20Mars%20Sample%20return%20mission%20and%20for%20de-orbiting%20satellites%20from%20low-Earth%20orbit%20-%20which%20will%20also%20help%20declutter%20the%20Space%20around%20Earth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733418120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F7ha0ehhg_isro-pslv-c59-mission-proba3-pti_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisro-puts-proba-3-in-orbit-a-10-point-guide-about-the-european-satellite-7181437%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20space%20agency%20ISRO%20today%20successfully%20launched%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency's%20PROBA-3%20satellite.%20The%20launch%20was%20on%20board%20ISRO's%20workhorse%20rocket%20-%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20or%20PSLV%20in%20its%2061st%20commercial%20mission%20'C-59'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisro-puts-proba-3-in-orbit-a-10-point-guide-about-the-european-satellite-7181437%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Physical%20Classes%20To%20Resume%20In%20Delhi%20Schools%20As%20Air%20Quality%20Improves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20(DoE)%20on%20Thursday%20issued%20a%20circular%20announcing%20the%20resumption%20of%20physical%20classes%20in%20all%20government%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20comes%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20permitted%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20to%20shift%20to%20Stage%20Two%20restrictions%20under%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20government%2C%20government-aided%2C%20and%20unaided%20recognised%20private%20schools%20under%20the%20DoE%2C%20NDMC%2C%20MCD%2C%20and%20Delhi%20Cantonment%20Board%20are%20required%20to%20conduct%20all%20classes%20in%20physical%20mode%20with%20immediate%20effect.%26quot%3B%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20approval%20to%20implement%20Stage%20T