%20GRAP%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%20as%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20required.%20According%20to%20CAQM%2C%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20has%20continuously%20improved%20since%20November%2024.%20An%20AQI%20of%20165%20was%20recorded%20today%2C%20making%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20'moderate'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20cautioned%20that%20the%20pollution%20restrictions%20under%20GRAP%202%20should%20still%20be%20in%20place%20to%20maintain%20the%20improved%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20does%20it%20mean%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20stage%202%20of%20GRAP%2C%20measures%20such%20as%20mechanised%20sweeping%20of%20roads%2C%20use%20of%20anti-smog%20guns%2C%20and%20sprinkling%20water%20daily%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20tackle%20dust%20with%20focused%20attention%20on%20identified%20air%20pollution%20hotspots.%20Power%20suppliers%20need%20to%20ensure%20uninterrupted%20supply%20so%20that%20the%20use%20of%20diesel%20generator%20sets%20can%20be%20minimised.%20Alerts%20will%20be%20issued%20through%20newspapers%2C%20television%2C%20and%20radio%20to%20advise%20people%20about%20air%20pollution%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%20doesn't%20slip%20into%20'very%20poor'%20or%20'severe'%20category%20again%2C%20people%20are%20advised%20to%20use%20public%20transport%20and%20ditch%20personal%20vehicles%20whenever%20possible.%20People%20are%20also%20requested%20to%20take%20a%20less%20congested%20route%20to%20their%20destination%20even%20if%20it%20is%20slightly%20longer%20along%20with%20regularly%20replacing%20air%20filters%20in%20their%20automobiles%20at%20recommended%20intervals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBan%20on%20the%20use%20of%20coal%20and%20firewood%20will%20still%20be%20in%20place%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20tandoors%20at%20restaurants%20and%20hotels.%20Use%20of%20diesel%20generators%20sets%20will%20also%20not%20be%20a