0ordered%20an%20investigation%20to%20confirm%20whether%20the%20drinking%20water%20was%20indeed%20contaminated.%20People%20in%20the%20area%20have%20been%20asked%20not%20to%20drink%20piped%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affected%20individuals%2C%20residing%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20Malaimedu%2C%20Mariamman%20Kovil%20Street%20and%20Muthalamman%20Kovil%20Street%2C%20were%20admitted%20to%20the%20Chromepet%20Government%20General%20Hospital%20and%20a%20private%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20have%20alleged%20that%20their%20health%20issues%20were%20caused%20by%20drinking%20water%20mixed%20with%20sewage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contamination%20has%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20area's%20water%20supply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Minister%20TM%20Anbarasan%20inspected%20the%20affected%20area%20and%20ordered%20the%20immediate%20setup%20of%20a%20medical%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty-three%20people%20have%20fallen%20ill%20and%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital.%20It%20is%20not%20yet%20known%20if%20the%20drinking%20water%20was%20contaminated.%20An%20investigation%20is%20also%20looking%20into%20whether%20the%20health%20issues%20were%20caused%20by%20the%20food%20they%20consumed.%20If%20the%20water%20was%20contaminated%2C%20the%20entire%20area%20would%20have%20been%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Minister%20said%20speaking%20to%20reporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20(EPS)%20expressed%20shock%20over%20the%20deaths.%20He%20condemned%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20ensure%20the%20supply%20of%20safe%20drinking%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20government%20to%20distribute%20safe%20drinking%20water%20to%20the%20people.%20They%20should%20have%20carefully%20examined%20whether%20drinking%20water%20was%20being%20supplied%20properly%20and%20without%20any%20contamination%20between%20drinking%20water%20and%20sewage%20pipes%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20cyclone's%20landfall%2C%26quot%3B%20EPS%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20criticised%20the%20government%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20condemn%20MK%20Stalin's%20government%20for%20its%20callousness%20that%20risked%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20for%20immediate%20measures%20to%20guarantee%20the%20supply%20of%20safe%20drinking%20water%20to%20all%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20Chief%20K%20Annamalai%20also%20criticised%20the%20state%20government's%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis.%20He%20questioned%20the%20efficacy%20of%20Minister%20Anbarasan's%20response%20and%20accused%20the%20minister%20of%20being%20dismissive%20by%20blaming%20residents%20for%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733412540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fb0l8lk5_tn-health-min-_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-die-near-chennai-after-drinking-sewage-laced-water-23-in-hospital-7180745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20people%20died%2C%20and%2023%20others%20fell%20ill%2C%20in%20Pallavaram%20near%20Chennai%20on%20Thursday%20after%20reportedly%20consuming%20drinking%20water%20contaminated%20with%20sewage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-die-near-chennai-after-drinking-sewage-laced-water-23-in-hospital-7180745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe%20Wasn't%20Drunk...%26quot%3B%3A%20On%20Kambli's%20Reunion%20With%20Tendulkar%2C%20Friend%20Clears%20Air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20from%20the%20unveiling%20of%20legendary%20cricket%20coach%20Ramakant%20Achrekar's%20memorial%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20ha