hey%20had%20weapons%2C%20stressing%20that%20my%20life%20was%20in%20danger.%20There%20were%207-8%20people%2C%20some%20drunk%2C%20shouting%20at%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kidnappers%20had%20asked%20him%20for%20a%20ransom%20of%20%E2%82%B9%2020%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CI%20called%20up%20many%20friends%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20collect%20the%20money%20and%20gave%20them%20%E2%82%B97.5-8%20lakh%20for%20my%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshah-rukh-khan-would-visit-slums-at-night-to-meet-his-staff-members-family-reveals-comedian-5832764%5C%22%3ESunil%20Pal%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CPolice%20have%20asked%20me%20to%20file%20a%20case.%20But%20I%20am%20under%20so%20much%20trauma.%20I%20don't%20know%20whether%20I%20will%20file%20the%20case%20or%20not.%20They%20didn't%20even%20give%20threats%20to%20me%2C%20but%20said%20they%20would%20cause%20harm%20to%20my%20family%20if%20I%20took%20any%20action%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Pal%20shot%20to%20fame%20after%20winning%20first%20prize%20in%20the%20stand-up%20comedy%20series%3Cem%3E%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Laughter%20Challenge%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202005.%20He%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20films%20like%3Cem%3E%20Bhavnao%20Ko%20Samjho%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fakshay-kumar-watches-fan-striking-his-iconic-pose-from-phir-hera-pheri-in-saudi-arabia-3576669%5C%22%3EPhir%20Hera%20Pheri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Apna%20Sapna%20Money%20Money%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EBombay%20to%20Goa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733409300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9ch148po_sunil-pal-_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsunil-pal-says-kidnappers-demanded-rs-20-lakh-7179327%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Pal%20revealed%20that%20the%20kidnappers%20left%20him%20on%20the%20Delho-Meerut%20road%20with%20only%2