tr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Mumbai%20%7C%20Actor%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20attends%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Video%20source%3A%20ANI%2F%20DG-IPR)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKS6Y8CMDFu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKS6Y8CMDFu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1864631328328831420%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20won%20230%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20emerging%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20state%20polls%20when%20the%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20November%2023.%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20-%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20-%20won%2057%20and%2041%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20or%20MVA%20-%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20-%20suffered%20a%20shattering%20loss.%20Their%20combined%20total%20stood%20at%20a%20paltry%2046%20seats.%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Sena%20faction%20won%2020%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2016%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20party%2C%20the%20other%20NCP%20faction%2C%20won%2010%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20serving%20as%20an%20obscure%20corporator%20to%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20mayor%20of%20Nagpur%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20has%20strengthened%20his%20status%20as%20a%20prominent%20leader%20within%20his%20party.%20He%20is%20only%20the%20second%20Brahmin%20to%20serve%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20following%20the%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Manohar%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESon%20of%20Jan%20Sangh%20and%20later%20BJP%20leader%20late%20Gangadhar%20Fadnavis%2C%20whom%20his%20fellow%20Nagpur%20politician