%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F132648%2Fct-meeting-all-set-for-the-hybrid-model-no-takers-for-pcb-demand-of-tri-series%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%20board%20members%20-%2015%20in%20all%20-%20are%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20hybrid%20model%20of%20hosting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPCB's%20demand%20is%20that%20if%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20hosted%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20then%20all%20ICC%20events%20hosted%20by%20Indian%20should%20also%20be%20hosted%20in%20the%20same%20style%20in%20the%20future.%20That%20demand%20will%20remain%20at%20the%20top%20of%20agenda%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20PCB%20might%20ask%20for%20compensation%20if%20five%20matches%20-%20India's%20three%20group%20matches%2C%20one%20semi-final%20and%20one%20final%20-%20are%20shifted%20to%20a%20neutral%20venue.%20There%20may%20not%20be%20any%20opposition%20to%20this%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20also%20reportedly%20asked%20for%20a%20tri-series%2C%20involving%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20another%20country%2C%20to%20be%20hosted%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue%20but%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20this%20demand%20is%20accepted%20or%20not.%20Currently%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20play%20each%20other%20only%20in%20ICC%20and%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20events.%20The%20report%20has%20said%20that%20this%20demand%20may%20also%20be%20rejected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20also%20said%20that%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20should%20be%20placed%20in%20different%20groups%20should%20a%20hybrid%20model%20is%20followed%2C%20so%20that%20the%20latter%20do%20not%20have%20to%20play%20any%20league%20match%20outside%20the%20country.%20The%20ICC%20is%20likely%20reject%20this%20demand%20too%20as%20an%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20match%20is%20the%20mo