od%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin%2C%20they%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOrient%20stranded%20boards%20are%20a%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin.%20They%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Edifice%20Consultant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20OSB%20wall%20panels%20helped%20us%20nullify%20the%20unwanted%20refraction%20and%20reverberation%20in%20the%20studio.%20Since%20the%20OSB%20panels%20are%20not%20as%20highly%20compressed%20as%20plywood%20they%20are%20excellent%20sound%20absorbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aameer%20adds.%20But%20the%20real%20magic%20lies%20in%20the%20matrix.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20raw%20finish%20of%20%5BOSB%E2%80%99s%5D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20strand%20composition%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds%20a%20subtle%20texture%20to%20the%20overall%20monochromatic%2C%20industrial-themed%20office%20space.%E2%80%9D%