%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20and%20Future%20Group%20clashed%20over%20a%20%243.4%20billion%20deal%20for%20Reliance%20to%20acquire%20Future%20Retail%E2%80%99s%20assets%2C%20which%20Amazon%20claimed%20violated%20its%20prior%20agreement%20granting%20rights%20over%20Future%20Group%E2%80%99s%20retail%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Emergency%20Arbitrator%20(EA)%2C%20with%20both%20parties%E2%80%99%20consent%2C%20barred%20FRL%20from%20transferring%20its%20assets%20on%20October%2025%2C%202020.%20FRL%20challenged%20this%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20where%20a%20Single%20Judge%20upheld%20the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20but%20the%20Division%20Bench%20later%20deemed%20it%20unenforceable.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%20under%20the%20Arbitration%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVodafone%20vs%20Indian%20Government%20(2020)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVodafone%20initiated%20arbitration%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20a%20%E2%82%B922%2C000%20crore%20retrospective%20tax%20demand%20introduced%20by%20a%202012%20amendment%20to%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20heard%20at%20the%20Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20concluded%20in%20Vodafone%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20ruling%20that%20the%20tax%20demand%20violated%20the%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%20India%20was%20directed%20to%20refund%20legal%20costs%20and%20abandon%20its%20claim%20for%20retrospective%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsumers%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20ADR%20measures%20due%20to%20the%20misconception%20that%20ADR%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20may%20not%20yield%20optimal%20results.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20entirely%20accurate.%20Better%20awareness%20is%20needed%20to%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20these%20measures%20for%20consumers%2