%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20several%20campaigns%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20anaemia%2C%20especially%20among%20pregnant%20women%20and%20young%20girls.%20Through%20Rural%20Health%20Educational%20Society%2C%20he%20started%20distributing%20iron%20tablets%2C%20conducting%20blood%20tests%2C%20and%20teaching%20about%20hygiene%2C%20gradually%20reducing%20maternal%20deaths%20and%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20thousands%20in%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20work%20in%20rural%20healthcare%20was%20flourishing%2C%20another%20calling%20beckoned%20Dr%20Praveen%2C%20one%20that%20came%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20Smt%20Sowbhagyavathi%20Garu.%20Having%20always%20believed%20that%20health%20is%20intrinsically%20linked%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20she%20encouraged%20her%20son%20to%20expand%20his%20vision%20to%20urban%20areas%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287374%2Fdelhi-ncr-fight-air-pollution-north-india-smog-health-risk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epollution%20and%20environmental%20degradation%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20becoming%20pressing%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20driven%20by%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20environmental%20conservation%2C%20Dr%20Praveen%20established%20the%20Bhagyanand%20Botanical%20Society%20in%20the%20urban%20landscape.%20The%20organisation%20focuses%20on%20environmental%20awareness%2C%20sustainable%20practices%2C%20and%20the%20conservation%20of%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20always%20taught%20me%20that%20good%20health%20starts%20with%20clean%20air%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20healthy%20surroundings.%20We%20cannot%20separate%20health%20from%20the%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Bhagyanand%20Botanical%20Society%2C%20Dr%20Praveen%20has%20championed%20several%20init