s%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%2C%20particularly%20SDG%207%3A%20Affordable%20and%20Clean%20Energy%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20%E2%80%9Censure%20access%20to%20affordable%2C%20reliable%2C%20sustainable%20and%20modern%20energy%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20promote%20cleaner%20transportation%2C%20the%20city%20has%20been%20expanding%20its%20network%20of%20cycling%20and%20pedestrian%20lanes%2C%20with%20over%201%2C000%20kilometres%20of%20these%20pathways%20now%20under%20construction.%20Public%20bike-sharing%20systems%20have%20also%20been%20rolled%20out%20across%20the%20city%2C%20with%20400%20stations%20available%20to%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20fume-free%20mobility%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunities%20need%20to%20start%20demanding%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20broader%20roads%20and%20better%20flyovers%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20demand%20clean%20air%20from%20our%20political%20class.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Spanish%20city%20has%20also%20placed%20significant%20emphasis%20on%20public%20transportation.%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20extensive%20public%20transit%20system%2C%20including%20buses%2C%20trams%2C%20and%20metro%20lines%2C%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20travel%20without%20relying%20on%20private%20cars.%20The%20city%20operates%20a%20number%20of%20initiatives%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20use%20public%20transport%20and%20adopt%20cleaner%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202135px)%20100vw%2C%202135px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Flast_11zon-1732805118.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tram%20in%20Barcelona%20traveling%20along